com.vectorprint.configuration.decoration

Class ParsingProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vectorprint.configuration.decoration.AbstractPropertiesDecorator
      • com.vectorprint.configuration.decoration.ParsingProperties
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EnhancedMap, Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,String[]>

    public class ParsingProperties
extends AbstractPropertiesDecorator
    This decorator supports loading properties from streams, urls or files and saving to a url.
    Author:
    Eduard Drenth at VectorPrint.nl
